column5: Noi recovered the winter Magic, #4C『#766IFrost Web』#1C!
The Moon Bird eggs have been placed.
Let's try changing the season to
Summer and coming back here again.
It should be safe for a bird's nest,
as long as as it's high enough to be
out of the reach of monsters.
This must be the perfect place
for Moon Birds to lay their eggs!
All right, I think we're good to go.
